<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SNS - Ministério da Saúde</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #006633 0%, #003300 100%);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 20px;
        }
        h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .badge {
            background: #ffcc00;
            color: #003300;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>🏥 SNS - Sistema Nacional de Saúde</h1>
        <p>Ministério da Saúde - República de Angola</p>
        <div class="badge">✅ Servidor funcionando!</div>
        <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Portal do Ministério em construção...</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>